OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,FA restaurant has published CCTV images
OL,7,Fof customers who ran up a bill of #230
OL,8,Fand left without paying.
OL,10,FThe diners ordered cocktails, spirits,
OL,11,Ffillet steaks and desserts at the
OL,12,FChadderton Bar and Grill, a
OL,13,FMediterranean restaurant in Chadderton
OL,14,Fnear Oldham and left without settling
OL,15,Fup.
OL,17,FOwner Lokman has described how they
OL,18,Fsneakily staggered their exit on
OL,19,FSaturday 14 February.
