OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,FPictures of the bill showed how the
OL,7,Fparty placed orders for two fillet
OL,8,Fsteaks, priced at #26.95 each, as well
OL,9,Fas pizzas and portions of Frederick's
OL,10,Fice cream, and drinks including Malibu
OL,11,Fand coke and eight pornstar martinis.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the Manchester Evening
OL,14,FNews, owner Lokman said the group
OL,15,Farrived without a booking at around
OL,16,F7pm.
OL,18,FHe said: "They hadn't booked and we
OL,19,Fwere quite busy. It was two ladies and
OL,20,Fone gentleman and they wanted a table
OL,21,Fbut had to wait.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
