OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,F"After 15 minutes they got a table and
OL,7,Forder cocktails, double Malbius, food
OL,8,Fand dessert. Their friend also came to
OL,9,Fjoin them. One girl went out first for
OL,10,Fa smoke, then the others followed
OL,11,Fafter about five minutes.
OL,13,F"I was serving another table taking an
OL,14,Forder, and the next thing, I looked
OL,15,Fover and they had disappeared.
OL,17,F"I am gutted. It's not just about the
OL,18,Fmoney, but it's the time. We had to
OL,19,Fmake all the cocktails for them when
OL,20,Fwe were busy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
