OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,FIn a public post on Facebook, along
OL,7,Fwith CCTV of the party leaving, the
OL,8,Fvenue wrote: "We are sharing this
OL,9,Fmessage to make other restaurant
OL,10,Fowners and businesses aware.
OL,12,F"These customers visited our
OL,13,Frestaurant, enjoyed their meal, and
OL,14,Funfortunately left without paying the
OL,15,Fbill. We have CCTV footage and the
OL,16,Fbill receipt as proof of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
