OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1771360684
OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,F"As a business, we normally respect
OL,7,Fcustomer privacy and never share CCTV
OL,8,Ffootage publicly. However, in this
OL,9,Fsituation, we feel it is important to
OL,10,Fraise awareness and protect other
OL,11,Flocal businesses from similar
OL,12,Fincidents.
OL,14,F"If the individuals in this video see
OL,15,Fthis post, we kindly request you to
OL,16,Fcontact us and settle the outstanding
OL,17,Fbill. We also request fellow business
OL,18,Fowners to stay alert. Thank you for
OL,19,Fyour support."
