OL,3,CRestaurant releases CCTV of diners who
OL,4,Cleft without paying #230 bill
OL,6,FAfter the post was shared, customers
OL,7,Fand followers were quick to respond,
OL,8,Fas one person wrote: "Oh this is
OL,9,Fhorrible, my family and myself have
OL,10,Fhad lovely meals here including xmas
OL,11,Fdinner. What is wrong with people.
OL,13,F"I feel like crying. You terrible
OL,14,Fpeople," as another responded: "How on
OL,15,Fearth in 2026 do people have the
OL,16,Faudacity to walk into establishments,
OL,17,Fsit down, eat a meal and walk out
OL,18,Fwithout paying. That is actually
OL,19,FMORTIFYING to think of."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
